extends layouts/default
block content

  //- Introduction Masthead
  section.intro
    .container
      h1 Vehicle Wraps &amp; Graphics
      h2 FLX Wraps is the premier large-format graphics and vehicle wrap specialists in Cayuga County. From design to installation, FLX Wraps gets it done right.

  //- Section: About FLX Wraps
  section#about.main.about
    .container
      .row
        .col-sm-8.about-content
          h2 About FLX
            span.thin Wraps
          p Based in Auburn, New York, <strong>FLX Wraps</strong> is a full service, large-format graphics and vehicle wrap company specializing in wall wraps, commercial fleet and personal vehicle graphics and more.
          p From design to print to installation, we help your message get to your customers from start to finish professionally and with top-notch service.
          ul.list-unstyled
            li
              h3.icon-check Full Wraps
              p The ultimate way to promote your brand on the road. From top to bottom, your vehicle will be decked out in a way that your customers will never miss.
            li
              h3.icon-check Half Wraps
              p The second-best marketing tool we offer. Your company's message will be sure to be seen with a beautifully designed half-wrap.
            li
              h3.icon-check Vinyl Graphics
              p On a budget? Vinyl graphics and lettering help you get your message across without a heavy up-front investment.
          a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg(href='#contact') Contact us today
        #quote.col-sm-4.sidebar-container
          form.form(method='POST', action='//formspree.io/ryan@imageagent.net')
            h2 Get a 
              span.thin Quote
            .form-group
              label(for='formName') Name *
              input#formName.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Enter your name', name='Name', required='')
            .form-group
              label(for='formEmail') Email Address *
              input#formEmail.form-control(type='email', placeholder='Enter your email', name='Email', required='')
            .form-group
              label(for='formVehicle') Vehicle Make &amp; Model *
              input#formVehicle.form-control(type='text', placeholder='e.g. Ford Transit', name='Vehicle', required='')
            .form-group
              label(for='formOptions') Wrap Type *
              select#formOptions.form-control(name='Wrap Type', required='')
                option(value='Full-Wrap') Full Wrap
                option(value='Half-Wrap') Half Wrap
                option(value='Vinyl Graphic') Vinyl Graphic
            input(type='hidden', name='_subject', value='FLX Wraps - Request for Quote')
            input(type='hidden', name='_next', value='http://flxwraps.com/thanks.html')
            input(type='text', name='_gotcha', style='display:none')
            input.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.btn-block(type='submit', value='Send me a quote')

  //- Section: Gauges
  section#gauges.main.stats
    .container
      h2 More bang for your 
        span.thin buck
      p Compared to traditional forms, vehicle wrap advertising is the most cost-effective.
      .row.heat-gauges
        .col-sm-4.stat
          h3 Vehicle Wrap
          .heat-gauge.low
          .stat-info
            h4#hg-price-low
            em Cost per thousand impressions
        .col-sm-4.stat
          h3 Television
          .heat-gauge.med
          .stat-info
            h4#hg-price-med
            em Cost per thousand impressions
        .col-sm-4.stat
          h3 Newspaper
          .heat-gauge.hi
          .stat-info
            h4#hg-price-hi
            em Cost per thousand impressions
      p.fine-print Statistics compiled by the Outdoor Advertising Association of America.

  //- Section: The Process
  section#process.main.process
    .container
      h2 How it 
        span.thin Works
      .row(style='margin:4em 0;')
        .col-sm-4.process-part
          .how-image
            img(src='images/how/how-design.png', alt='Design')
          h3 Design
          p With our backgrounds in design and marketing, we do not stop until we’ve got an effective and eye-catching vehicle wrap based around your target audience and your marketing goals.
        .col-sm-4.process-part
          .how-image
            img(src='images/how/how-print.png', alt='Print')
          h3 Print
          p Once we have an approved design, it’s time to print it. Your graphics are ready in about 3-5 business days. We use 3M and Arlon vehicle wrap vinyl with overlaminate, which we include on all wraps.
        .col-sm-4.process-part
          .how-image
            img(src='images/how/how-install.png', alt='Install')
          h3 Install
          p Our professional installers will clean you vehicle and take care to ensure proper application of your vinyl wrap or decals. After 1-3 days, your vehicle will be ready to make a statement on the road.

