  //- Section: Contact Us
  section#contact.main.contact
    .container
      .row
        .col-sm-8
          h2 FAQ
            span(style='text-transform:none;') s
          #accordion.panel-group(role='tablist', aria-multiselectable='true')
            // One
            .panel.panel-default
              a(data-toggle='collapse', data-parent='#accordion', href='#collapseOne', aria-expanded='false', aria-controls='collapseOne')
                #headingOne.panel-heading(role='tab')
                  h4.panel-title How much do vehicle wraps cost?
              #collapseOne.panel-collapse.collapse.in(role='tabpanel', aria-labelledby='headingOne')
                .panel-body Every vehicle &amp; application is different, so price really depends on the scope of your vehicle wrap project. Vehicle wraps can range from $800 - $4,000. For a more precise quote, contact us with more information about your wrap project.
            // Two
            .panel.panel-default
              a(data-toggle='collapse', data-parent='#accordion', href='#collapseTwo', aria-expanded='false', aria-controls='collapseTwo')
                #headingTwo.panel-heading(role='tab')
                  h4.panel-title Do I have to get a full wrap or do I have other options?
              #collapseTwo.panel-collapse.collapse(role='tabpanel', aria-labelledby='headingTwo')
                .panel-body We work with your budget to get you the most advertising for your dollar. You can do just windows, or partial wraps. One option is to start out with just perforated window graphic and then add to it as your business grows to make a complete wrap.
            // Three
            .panel.panel-default
              a(data-toggle='collapse', data-parent='#accordion', href='#collapseThree', aria-expanded='false', aria-controls='collapseThree')
                #headingThree.panel-heading(role='tab')
                  h4.panel-title Does a vehicle wrap damage your paint?
              #collapseThree.panel-collapse.collapse(role='tabpanel', aria-labelledby='headingThree')
                .panel-body No, a car wrap, when applied and removed correctly by a professional installer, will actually protect your paint.
            // Four
            .panel.panel-default
              a(data-toggle='collapse', data-parent='#accordion', href='#collapseFour', aria-expanded='false', aria-controls='collapseFour')
                #headingFour.panel-heading(role='tab')
                  h4.panel-title How durable is a vinyl wrap?
              #collapseFour.panel-collapse.collapse(role='tabpanel', aria-labelledby='headingFour')
                .panel-body Every vehicle wrap is laminated after printing. This helps to protect the wrap. It comes in Matte or Gloss finish. The majority of vehicle wraps last for 3 to 5 years, but there is no guarantee. We do, however, offer the 3 year manufacturer’s warranty.
            // Five
            .panel.panel-default
              a(data-toggle='collapse', data-parent='#accordion', href='#collapseFive', aria-expanded='false', aria-controls='collapseFive')
                #headingFive.panel-heading(role='tab')
                  h4.panel-title Can you wrap my boat? What about a plane?
              #collapseFive.panel-collapse.collapse(role='tabpanel', aria-labelledby='headingFive')
                .panel-body If it exists, we'll wrap it.
            // Six
            .panel.panel-default
              a(data-toggle='collapse', data-parent='#accordion', href='#collapseSix', aria-expanded='false', aria-controls='collapseSix')
                #headingSix.panel-heading(role='tab')
                  h4.panel-title How much do you charge for a vehicle wrap design?
              #collapseSix.panel-collapse.collapse(role='tabpanel', aria-labelledby='headingSix')
                .panel-body Our hourly rate for design and revisions is $75.00 an hour.
